hopobject.body: How much will it cost to send this letter to ? bluefusion bluetooth toyota Most students at Glendale Community College in Glendale, Calif. drive to school, says Patricia Hurley, financial aid director at the school. While there is public transportation, commuting by public bus could require students to transfer several times during a 10-mile commute. And for some students, it could still cost as much as $90 per month.
